Introduction

Yui is a Japanese trainee under H1GHR MUSIC. She is a member of the agency's upcoming girl group along three other I-LAND2: N/a contestants.

In 2024, Yui was a contestant on Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she was sadly eliminated in episode 7. At that time, she was a trainee under WAKEONE.
